Package: SimpLin
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kai", "Jeffreys", , "kai.jeffreys@colostate.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Runs a simple linear regression. Inputs two vectors, a predictor
    and a response, and outputs a list containing relevant information about the
    regression and regression coefficients. Depends on Rcpp and therefore will be
    computationally quicker than other regression functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
